data.description: Lovely open-concept home in desireable neighborhood - Burleson ISD! Spacious 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 2 car garage, 2 living areas, and 2 dining areas. Custom cherry kitchen cabinetry with huge island and breakfast area. Master suite is downstairs; master bath has dual sinks, garden tub, separate shower, and huge walk-in closet. Storage galore throughout! Oversized laundry room, walk-in pantry, and lots of closets. Covered back patio for relaxing.
